Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: China denies move to capitalism
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xgct
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Dec 1984
Good news or bad news? China's main daily newspaper rebuked for 'flawed' story of the country's potential move to a capitalist economy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less